                            <comment id="481124" author="JIRAUSER18444" created="Thu, 11 Dec 2025 16:20:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rather than update the test to sleep for an extra second, an alternative could be to update the timestamp comparisons like this:&lt;/p&gt;
